"""FileID: 4b681970-4c82-4bcf-8c93-2d04fe082ad1"""
class KeyErrors(object):
    """ID: c25abe04-fb74-4d67-ae2f-18704d20c6ad"""
    def __init__(self):
        """ID: 259c9c8d-6723-4813-93c7-924151b64877"""
        self.key_errs = []

    def add(self, filename, lineno, namespace, key):
        """ID: a627267a-45e1-413e-9954-a168f7f1e39c"""
        self.key_errs.append({
            "filename": filename,
            "lineno": lineno,
            "namespace": namespace,
            "key": key
        })

    def get(self):
        """ID: c2da9dba-0058-4ae4-a118-e40b07013861"""
        return self.key_errs
